## Footnote

Use [^footnote number]

Here is a sample footnote[^1].

Footnotes can have multiple lines too[^2].

Here is a simple footnote[^1].

A footnote can also have multiple lines[^2]. To add line breaks within a footnote, prefix new lines with 2 spaces.
  This is a second line.

