## Automatic Link

GitHub automatically creates links when valid URLs are written in a comment.

For example:
<https://www.webfx.com/tools/emoji-cheat-sheet/>

To see how it works, see [Alerts](#alerts).

---

### Relative links

<a id="rela-link"></a>

[!NOTE]Note the message no-inline-html.

Relative links make locating the linked enitity easier. Link is set from whichever branch you are in.\ or ..\ is added to set relative link.

